tournament.name: Tivoli presents Tuesday Taps Episode 27
tournament.description:
Tivoli Outlaw Beer is sponsoring tonight with a pint of their Outlaw Lager. They will be purchasing a pint each to the first 15 players that arrive at Free Play Dallas for our Killer Queen tournament. (Be sure to check in with host and show us your registration page).

The DraftMixer tradition can never die in Dallas with Tuesday Taps at Free Play Dallas! Signups and casuals are free until 8pm, new players 100% welcome. Then teams are drafted (or computer mixed for skill) and we compete in a double elimination bracket (8pm) streamed live at Twitch.tv/fpkql. Each member of the winning team gets 8,000 rewards points in the Free Play Loyalty Club https://freeplayinc.com/club , a Polaroid with the team, and the adulation of all Killer Queen players in attendance.
tournament.registration_message:
Register for free, just click through any payment options.  This will track your tournament stats as well as let you dictate exactly how you are called to the cab by the overlay.

Please list "Free Agent" as your team.
